						<Synopsis>The command selects the operation performed by the scaling function.
The query returns the operation performed by the scaling function.</Synopsis>
						<HelpLinks>
							<HelpLink name=":CALCulate:SCALe:FUNCtion" endAnchor="GAIN" url="__I_SCPI\CALCulate_SCALe_Subsystem.htm#FUNCtion" />
