						<Synopsis>The command disables or enables the beep heard during continuity, diode, or probe hold measurements, or when an error is generated from the front panel or remote interface.</Synopsis>
						<HelpLinks>
							<HelpLink name=":SYSTem:BEEPer:STATe" endAnchor="CLIC-STAT" url="__I_SCPI\SYSTem_General Commands.htm#BEEP-STAT" />
