					<Node mnemonic="MAC">
						<SubsystemCommand>
							<Synopsis>The query returns the instrument's Media Access Control (MAC) address as an ASCII string of 12 hexadecimal characters (0-9 and A-F) enclosed in quotation marks.</Synopsis>
